      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot </strong>to a medium bowl with<strong> half</strong> the <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!),<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong>,<strong> </strong>and a splash of<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>warm water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong></p>",
