    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped coriander </strong>to a<strong> food processor </strong>with the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped shallot </strong>and blitz until combined</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining white wine vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and blitz to a coarse paste – this is your <strong>coriander chutney</strong></p><p>Tip: No food processor? Chop everything up as finely as you can and mix it together!</p>",
