    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces and pat dry again</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
