    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> <strong>rotis </strong>to a baking tray (or two!) and top<strong> </strong>with the<strong> torn mozzarella</strong>, <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong>, <strong>coriander chutney</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Place the <strong>remaining rotis</strong> on top so you end up with 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> roti sandwiches</p><p>Top each<strong> </strong>roti sandwich with a small knob of<strong> butter</strong></p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 8-10 min or until the cheese is melted – these are your <strong>Mumbai-style toasties</strong></p>",
