    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rotis are cooking, dice the<strong> cucumber</strong> finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>tomatoes</strong> finely</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped cucumber </strong>and <strong>chopped tomatoes </strong>to the bowl with the <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong> and stir together – this is your <strong>kachumber salad</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>mayo </strong>to a separate small bowl<strong> </strong>and<strong> </strong>swirl the<strong> mango chutney </strong>through (don’t fully mix) – this is your <strong>mango mayo</strong></p>",
