      "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> Mumbai-style toasties </strong>into quarters</p><p>Drain the <strong>kachumber salad</strong>, discard the liquid</p><p>Serve the <strong>Mumbai-style stuffed rotis</strong> with the <strong>nigella fries</strong>, <strong>kachumber salad</strong> and <strong>mango mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
